<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Description</strong> = A description of each category.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Meta title</strong> = A text that should be displayed as the tab title in the web browser and in the search engine results.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Visible</strong> = Whether I want the individual categories to be included in the sitemap.</p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>1 = Yes, the category should be included in the sitemap.<br>
0 = No, the category should <em>not</em> be included in the sitemap.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In this example, I only want the first two category levels to be included in the sitemap. I’ve inserted the numbers 1 and 0 accordingly.</p>
</div>
</li>
